2017 / 2018 Council services available to schools

This site sets out to detail council services for schools to purchase. You can view all services that are available for this financial year, and place an order for those you are interested in.

Most services are available to schools outside the London Borough of Barnet.  If yours is a school outside Barnet and you wish to subscribe to any of these services, please make contact with the individual service providers directly to check availability.

Find traded services

We can help you get the services you need for your school. You can search for a specific service, or browse all available traded services and see what's available this year.

More about traded services

  • Browse all traded services
  • Ordering traded services
  • Statutory service requirements

Looking for more info about services for schools?

Find links to your traded services systems and useful information for schools in Barnet.

View useful links

Need help ordering services for schools?

Get answers to questions about how to order services, amending an order, etc. by contacting the Barnet Schools team.
